.TH "brcmf_p2p_scan_prep" 9 "brcmf_p2p_scan_prep" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
brcmf_p2p_scan_prep \- prepare scan based on request.
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" brcmf_p2p_scan_prep
.BI "(struct wiphy *wiphy "  ","
.BI "struct cfg80211_scan_request *request "  ","
.BI "struct brcmf_cfg80211_vif *vif "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "wiphy" 12
wiphy device.
.IP "request" 12
scan request from cfg80211.
.IP "vif" 12
vif on which scan request is to be executed.
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Prepare the scan appropriately for type of scan requested. Overrides the
escan .\fBrun\fP callback for peer-to-peer scanning.
